In [5]:
plot.cov <- function(scaff,scaffan,vfrom,vto)
    {
        alTrack <- AlignmentsTrack(bamFile, chromosome=scaff, genome = 'enterofsc', name="Coverage")
        annTrack <- AnnotationTrack(start=scaffan$start, width=scaffan$with, chromosome=scaff, strand=scaffan$strand, id=scaffan$id, genome = "enterofsc", name = "ORFs")
        plotTracks(c(axisTrack,annTrack,alTrack), from = vfrom, to = vto, featureAnnotation = "id", chromosome = scaff, type="coverage",fontcolor.item='black')
    }
